#### 3. **No HTTPS/TLS Enforcement (OWASP A02:2021 - Cryptographic Failures)**
**Severity:** HIGH

**Issue:** The application doesn't enforce HTTPS, making data transmission vulnerable to man-in-the-middle (MITM) attacks.

**Recommendation:**
```javascript
const express = require('express');
const https = require('https');
const fs = require('fs');
const app = express();

// Enforce HTTPS in production
if (process.env.NODE_ENV === 'production') {
  app.use((req, res, next) => {
    if (req.header('x-forwarded-proto') !== 'https') {
      res.redirect(`https://${req.header('host')}${req.url}`);
    } else {
      next();
    }
  });
}

// Or use HSTS header
